des: "This very healthy breakfast or anytime beverage is loaded with antioxidants, potassium, protein, and fiber! I buy my strawberries fresh and then place them in a freezer safe container and freeze them. No ice is needed due to the frozen strawberries! Pour into a tall chilled glass and enjoy!"
ins: Blend strawberries, soy milk, banana, agave nectar, flax seed, and vanilla extract in a blender until creamy.
